>\n1965年日本向南泡賠償現金3.64億美元，貨款4億幾美元，係美元喎，附屬條件同德國對希臘一樣係永久解決，但係其後南泡歷屆政府都冇兌現承諾<br />\n<br />\n2015年重有46個慰安婦，韓國政府又要求3億日元，安倍一開始還價1億日元，後尾日本一炮過賠10億日元，並由安倍再行正式道歉，南泡就要撤走日本領事館前面嗰個慰安婦像，其他慰安婦像唔使撤銷<br />\n<br />\n依家協議又簽完喇，慰安婦攞咗錢喇，南泡兌現承諾未？冇，佢哋反而變本加厲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9e144d11b4c94a54a8c9a18810d6ab43cb52e2","tid":372811,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好撚賤 姦完人話人係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連當時美軍都話係雞，仲要係報告話「以日本人及高加索人標準來看，不漂亮」</blockquote><br />\n以前啲日本人邊忽靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定還是覺得啲鳯眼先係東方美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，大月薰都幾好樣，打扮下應該好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d59ee03e8e6fc81d6856cae486d9c292bac352f","tid":372811,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同樣係戰敗國，你睇下德國？錯就要認，打就企定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n德國有咩錯？  錯在佢戰敗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n種族滅絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩錯??</blockquote><br />\n無，清滅準噶爾族就係英明決定，好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dd685131cba7799b40d62e68e3e84a17a3fec1","tid":372811,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquo