同支那狗本是同根生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔一個海個人格都差天共地<br />\n無賴生番對有承信嘅侵略者"},{"pid":"9c05b01a6f04c356a90be5518636e37ca70b9153","tid":372811,"uid":35460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca6d142d5e642903e2eef3437b1ac435be3c4b58","tid":372811,"uid":353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樣係戰敗國，你睇下德國？錯就要認，打就企定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戰敗=錯<br />\n有無諗過去驗腦"},{"pid":"0b8c913afba9dafc01fda5663427c30b6f12f29f","tid":372811,"uid":120662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同樣係戰敗國，你睇下德國？錯就要認，打就企定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戰敗=錯<br />\n有無諗過去驗腦</blockquote><br />\n其實戰敗真係等於錯 <br />\n其實唔只德國有種族滅絕 蘇聯都有對猶太人進行大清洗<br />\n唔只d日本人有強姦，蘇聯打進柏林嘅過程都強姦唔少女人<br />\n打仗時發生嘅野真係唔可以用和平世代嘅標準去量度"},{"pid":"b0db177c0f451583697ea8547f02f5bff8d2c11d","tid":372811,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T06:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n德國有咩錯？  錯在佢戰敗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前西德總理Willy Brandt<br />\n訪問 波蘭 途中 係波蘭猶太人紀念碑前雙膝下跪<br />\n勃蘭特下跪了，德意志卻站了起來。</blockquote><br />\n日本賠咗n次錢俾泡菜<br />\n德國賠咗幾多錢俾希臘？答案係零<img src=\"/a